text: Effie is a given name, usually feminine. Effie may also refer to: ==Places in the United States== * Effie, Louisiana, an unincorporated community * Effie, Minnesota, a city * Effie (unorganized territory), Minnesota * Effie, Mississippi, an unincorporated community * Effie, West Virginia, an unincorporated community * Lake Effie, Florida ==Other uses== * Effie (film), a biopic about Effie Gray * Effie: Just Quietly, a 2001 Australian satirical television series * Effie, the automated ironing machine.
